As you can see, we get Elemental dire charm. Please, ALL the mages who understand how stupid of an idea this is, let us ALL stand up, unite and protest before they even remotely thinking of adding another totally useless aa ability to our list. And by these mages, I mean those that were skeptic about Elemental Charm, and who turned out being correct ( I was not one of those - but I learn from my errors ). And to the others, who still believe that we should see the ability in game before we can judge it, remember that once it will be in game, getting it fixed/changed will be close to impossible.
<br />
